PARAMOUNT E-MART — FEATURE OVERVIEW

A production-grade PWA e-commerce platform for premium electronics retail.

CORE FEATURES
  • Product catalogue: categories, search, share links, slideshows
  • Age-restricted categories: 18+ verification with 4-hour session
  • Multi-gateway checkout: Flutterwave · OPay · Crypto (USDT/BTC/ETH)
  • Live shipment tracking: global satellite map (Leaflet + Esri)
  • Support ticket system with WhatsApp + Google Sheets notification
  • Online courses marketplace with enrollment + share links
  • Support, Contact, Receipt — all rendered as in-page popups
  • Google Sheets — ALL forms auto-sync (checkout, support, age, newsletter)
  • Foundation-style admin: 11 tabs, full CRUD, shipment editor, age admin
  • PWA: offline via Service Worker, installable on mobile + desktop
  • Bulk discount tiers + promo code engine
  • Age verification: pesVerifying() loader, 30-day persistent record

